{"title":"Discord 斜線指令","uid":"c66902af82d58e5380747693b3701622","slug":"discord-slash-command","date":"2021-08-26T23:53:52.000Z","updated":"2023-01-01T12:02:02.654Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/discord-slash-command.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.ibb.co/k5L4hcN/discord-cover.jpg","content":"<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">小提示</p>\n<p>此文案是從我的 Gitbook 搬運過來的，現在它不再被使用。</p>\n</div>\n<p>斜線指令（Slash commands）是近期 Discord 的大勢所趨，所謂的斜線指令，並<strong>不是指一般輸入如 <code>/start</code> 等指令，而是自動完成選單</strong>。</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"安裝-slash-command\"><a href=\"#安裝-slash-command\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安裝 slash-command\"></a>安裝 slash-command</h1><p>在編寫斜線指令前，我們必須要安裝 <code>slash-command</code>。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">pip install discord-py-slash-command</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">注意</p>\n<p>需要 Python 版本為 3.6 或以上，方可安裝。</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"為程序匯入資源庫\"><a href=\"#為程序匯入資源庫\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"為程序匯入資源庫\"></a>為程序匯入資源庫</h1><p>要實現斜線指令，我們主要需要匯入 <code>SlashCommand</code> 和 <code>SlashContext</code> 資源庫。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">from discord import Client, Intents, Embed\nfrom discord_slash import SlashCommand, SlashContext</code></pre>\n\n<p>匯入好了，現在就可以編寫斜線指令了。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">client &#x3D; commands.Bot(intents &#x3D; intents)\nslash &#x3D; SlashCommand(client, sync_commands &#x3D; True)</code></pre>\n\n<p>我們試試斜線指令的強大功能吧。</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"實現斜線指令\"><a href=\"#實現斜線指令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"實現斜線指令\"></a>實現斜線指令</h1><hr>\n<h2 id=\"基本使用\"><a href=\"#基本使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基本使用\"></a>基本使用</h2><p>例如，我們實現 <code>/hello</code> 指令，當我們輸入這指令，機器人便會發出嵌入式訊息 <code>Embed</code>。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">@slash.slash(description &#x3D; &quot;Say Hello&quot;)\nasync def hello(ctx: SlashContext):\n    e &#x3D; Embed(title &#x3D; &quot;Hello&quot;)\n    await ctx.send(embed &#x3D; e)</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">注意</p>\n<p>不是用 <code>@client.command()</code> 而是要用 <code>@slash.slash()</code>。參數 <code>ctx</code> 需要以 <code>SlashContext</code> 方式定義。</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"自動完成參數\"><a href=\"#自動完成參數\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"自動完成參數\"></a>自動完成參數</h2><p><code>/hello</code> 指令只是純粹的輸出訊息，要不我們試試<strong>自動完成參數</strong>的功能？假設我們要編寫消除訊息的指令。</p>\n<p>指令的概念大概是這樣的：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">消除訊息(20);</code></pre>\n\n<p>利用<strong>操作碼</strong>和<strong>操作數</strong>的概念，完成消除訊息指令的編寫程序。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>操作碼：消除訊息()<br>操作數：20</p></blockquote>\n<p>所以會編寫這樣子：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">@slash.slash(description &#x3D; &quot;Clear Messages&quot;)\nasync def clear(ctx: SlashContext, amount &#x3D; 100):\n    await ctx.channel_purge(limit &#x3D; amount)</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">小提示</p>\n<p><code>amount</code> 所貯存的值最終賦值於 <code>limit</code> 裏，所以可理解為限制數量。<br>如 <code>amount = 10</code>，則限制最多只可消除 10 次訊息。</p>\n</div>\n<p>現在我們就試試輸入 <code>/clear</code> 找出選單內的指令，完成自動完成程序吧。</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote danger\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M19.76 5.23C15.84 5.23 12 2 12 2C12 2 8.15996 5.23 4.23996 5.23C4.23996 5.23 1.86996 16.99 12 22C22.13 16.99 19.76 5.23 19.76 5.23Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 16H12\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">特别注意</p>\n<p>在沒有編寫斜線指令的機器人前，若機器人仍然在伺服器，即使編寫了斜線指令，亦<strong>不會立即更新程序編碼</strong>，你需要把機器人從伺服器中移除並踢出，方可更新斜線指令。</p>\n<p>當你為斜線指令實現了新的指令，都不會因此而更新，斜線指令會<strong>每一小時自動更新一次</strong>，所以請確保機器人<strong>長期處於啟動的狀態</strong>，方可達到定時更新的效果。</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<p>那就大功告成了。</p>\n","text":" 小提示 此文案是從我的 Gitbook 搬運過來的，現在它不再被使用。 斜線指令（Slash commands）是近期 Discord 的大勢所趨，所謂的斜線指令，並不是指一般輸入如 /start 等指令，而是自動完成選單。 安裝 slash-command在編寫斜線指令前，我...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.5k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Discord 開發","slug":"Discord-開發","count":4,"path":"api/categories/Discord-開發.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Python","slug":"Python","count":4,"path":"api/tags/Python.json"},{"name":"終端機指令","slug":"終端機指令","count":6,"path":"api/tags/終端機指令.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D-slash-command\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安裝 slash-command</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%82%BA%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E5%8C%AF%E5%85%A5%E8%B3%87%E6%BA%90%E5%BA%AB\"><span class=\"toc-text\">為程序匯入資源庫</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AF%A6%E7%8F%BE%E6%96%9C%E7%B7%9A%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">實現斜線指令</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">基本使用</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%87%AA%E5%8B%95%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E5%8F%83%E6%95%B8\